    <!-- http://www.cenitmio.es/ontologies/Location.owl#NAryRelationHasLocation -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.cenitmio.es/ontologies/Location.owl#NAryRelationHasLocation">
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Class created to support the nary relation among located entities, coordinates and temporal entities.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Punto de extensión para enlazar la localización con el tiempo en la red.

Especificar este naria con &quot;NAryRelationHasLocationAtTime&quot;.

Especificar la relación &quot;hasLocation&quot; con &quot;hasLocationAtTime&quot; que ira de  &quot;NAryRelationHasLocationAtTime&quot; a &quot;TimeInterval U TimeInstant&quot;.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">N-ary relation has location</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


